Package stratpoint.samuelnieva.EntityLayer

Class ProductEntity

java.lang.Object
stratpoint.samuelnieva.EntityLayer.ProductEntity
public class ProductEntity extends Object
The Product class contains information related to a product which can then be searched for, added and deleted from the lists in the Cart and Catalog classes.
